# Rain and Wetness

A first sanity check of the propositional core. // inline comments use //

prop p : It is raining
prop q : The ground is wet

claim C1 : p -> q

// A truth table for the named claim:
table C1

// Classic tautology and contradiction:
table p or not p
table p and not p

// Material implication really is equivalent to "not p, or q":
check C1 equivalent (not p or q)
